OL,3,C'Cult' priest assaulted 'staggering
OL,4,Cnumber' of women, court told
OL,6,FA priest who ran a "cult-like" church
OL,7,Fgroup sexually assaulted a "staggering
OL,8,Fnumber" of female members, a court has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FChristopher Brain, 68, is accused of
OL,12,Fabusing 13 women as leader of the
OL,13,Fevangelical movement the Nine O'Clock
OL,14,FService in Sheffield.
OL,16,FBrain, from Wilmslow, Cheshire, denies
OL,17,Fone count of rape and 36 counts of
OL,18,Findecent assault between 1981 and 1995.
