OL,3,C'Cult' priest assaulted 'staggering
OL,4,Cnumber' of women, court told
OL,6,FOpening the trial at at Inner London
OL,7,FCrown Court, prosecutor Tim Clark KC
OL,8,Ftold jurors that the Nine O'Clock
OL,9,FService (NOS) was aimed at younger
OL,10,Fpeople and "presented itself to the
OL,11,Foutside world as a progressive force
OL,12,Ffor good".
OL,14,F"In truth NOS became a closed and
OL,15,Fcontrolled group which the defendant
OL,16,Fdominated and abused his position
OL,17,Ffirst as a leader and then as an
OL,18,Fordained priest to sexually assault a
OL,19,Fstaggering number of women from his
OL,20,Fcongregation," he said.
