OL,6,FThe court heard some members gave up
OL,7,Ftheir inheritances and others their
OL,8,Fhomes.
OL,10,FThe prosecutor said those deemed
OL,11,Finsufficiently faithful and co-
OL,12,Foperative were ostracised from the
OL,13,Fgroup. Members became "terrified" of
OL,14,Fbeing excluded.
OL,16,FThe court heard a "homebase team" was
OL,17,Fset up to "care for" Brain who were
OL,18,Freferred to as "the Lycra Lovelies" or
OL,19,F"the Lycra Nuns".
