OL,6,FWomen who did not keep the defendant
OL,7,Fhappy would find themselves estranged
OL,8,Ffrom the group, Mr Clark said.
OL,10,FTV programmes were made and books
OL,11,Fwritten about NOS after some
OL,12,Fallegations were made in 1995 around
OL,13,FBrain's alleged abuse of position, the
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
OL,16,FBrain appeared in one of the
OL,17,Fdocumentaries and made admissions to
OL,18,Fthe filmmaker of sexual contact with a
OL,19,Fnumber of the female members of NOS,
OL,20,Fjurors were told.
