OL,6,FThe court heard Brain accepts he
OL,7,Fengaged in sexual activity with some
OL,8,Fof the complainants but that it was
OL,9,Fconsensual.
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said: "In short, the
OL,12,Fdefence case appears to be, to quote
OL,13,Ffrom the Life Of Brian, Brian Cohen's
OL,14,Fmother: 'He's not the Messiah, he's
OL,15,Fjust a very naughty boy'.
OL,17,F"The Crown state it was more than
OL,18,Fthat, the defendant created the
OL,19,Fatmosphere that allowed him to abuse a
OL,20,Fseries of women."
