OL,6,FJurors had been warned by the judge to
OL,7,Fcast emotion aside after the full list
OL,8,Fof charges was read to them ahead of
OL,9,Fthe opening.
OL,11,FJudge Freya Newbery said: "It may be
OL,12,Fthat what you have heard has initially
OL,13,Fupset you or perhaps revolted you or
OL,14,Ftouched a nerve of some sort.
OL,16,F"Any emotion that you feel, it really
OL,17,Fneeds to be put to one side while you
OL,18,Ffocus on your crucial work as a jury."
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
